Detailed Description

Provides a class method for parsing data downloaded from del.icio.us API posts/all requests into the localMoc of a given extore.

Parses given data downloaded from del.icious, obtaining, optionally: posts and tags, dates and/or bundles.

Parameters:
data 
doStarks If YES, bookmarks and tags are parsed from data and inserted into the localMoc of the extore.
doDates Switches on a function which is not implemented at this time.
doBundles Switches on a function which is not implemented at this time.
extore The extore into whose localMoc any bookmarks and tags found will be inserted as starks, and whose browfile's browid the exid of each inserted stark will be associated with.
lastUpdateTime Pointer to an NSDate* or NULL.  If not NULL, and a last update time is found while parsing the data, an NSDate representing this time will be assigned to this pointer.
error Pointer to an NSError* or NULL.  If not NULL, and an error occurs, an NSError explaining the error will be assigned to this pointer.
Returns:
YES if the operation completes with no error, otherwise NO.
